{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require action to make the roads safer for motorbikes",
        "additional_details": "I have recently started riding a motorbike, and trying to navigate around road markings, manhole covers as well as potholes makes riding more dangerous than it needs to be.\r\nWe are already at more risk from harm, we do not need the risks made higher by something that can be avoided.",
        "background": "Requiring the use of gritted paint for road markings could help ensure the rider doesn't slide on them.\r\nApplying grit to all manhole covers could help make them safe for motorbikes to ride over without the chance of slipping",
